{"tid":1931661,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"尊重版權 停止抄襲 黃台之瓜 何堪再摘？","createTime":"2020-03-18T09:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T10:36:03.000Z","uid":352040,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b284b21711ae11b5f048e50dd632ae364012366b","tid":1931661,"uid":352040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"在連登，巴絲不時會看到部分人搬字過紙，轉載圖片。抄襲其他網站的資料，會影響這些網站的收入，亦令大家心愛的連登蒙上「抄登」之污名。<br />\n<br />\n以蘋果日報為例，巴絲每次貼上蘋果日報的圖文，就等同減低蘋果日報網站的瀏覽量。其母公司壹傳媒已連年虧損，最新公布的收入亦按年下跌約百分之十六。黃台之瓜，巴絲難道忍心再摘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，我亦要在此譴責抄襲連登帖文的內容農場。你們行為卑劣，毫不尊重原創者，令人極度反感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位尊重版權，停止抄襲。「抄登」是其他「登」，不是我們連登。共勉之。<br />\n<br />\n*為考好中文，我用了書面語。巴絲加油呀！<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20191118/2V53BAQSGGDNLSIJAQYNJURQGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191118%2F2V53BAQSGGDNLSIJAQYNJURQGQ%2F&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=c97b8206\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191118%2F2V53BAQSGGDNLSIJAQYNJURQGQ%2F&h=7e0016b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20191118/2V53BAQSGGDNLSIJAQYNJURQGQ/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/126988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F126988&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=9aad2357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/126988</a>"},{"pid":"7051b9c50e2ae723eaa7ced4eada3bb2c774c8dc","tid":1931661,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"抄登係因為抄高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f80340b5f4666624c63d6bc5d32bbd82af74d85","tid":1931661,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7542e2deaf7cfcb3b14b17ba8c4ca53827f74e97","tid":1931661,"uid":352040,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7051b9c50e2ae723eaa7ced4eada3bb2c774c8dc","tid":1931661,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"抄登係因為抄高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"這是其中一個原因。抄襲其他網站內容是另一個。"},{"pid":"ae761f09e5534d46f1d8df36d08b757c750c80a1","tid":1931661,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932944\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932944</a><br />\n<br />\n我地已經比人抄到灰哂機<br />\n想請巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5964072e1031be8dd55ca3397963de78f35d97fe","tid":1931661,"uid":352040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae761f09e5534d46f1d8df36d08b757c750c80a1","tid":1931661,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932944\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932944</a><br />\n<br />\n我地已經比人抄到灰哂機<br />\n想請巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"支持你！所有人都要停止抄襲！"},{"pid":"daa80b26dc4afb47943fcd78ca1b8f7ce4e10132","tid":1931661,"uid":352040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl